title: Rimfire (1949 Noir Western) Every Man's Back Was A Target For His VENGEANCE!

sources.title: Rimfire (1949 Noir Western) Every Man's Back Was A Target For His VENGEANCE!
sources.description:
A ghostly gambler, a deadly secret, and a town on edge. Haunted by the ghost of a gambler, a remote town is on the brink of panic. A determined deputy must unravel a series of crimes to bring peace back to the troubled community, but the truth is more dangerous than he could have imagined. 

Original title: Rimfire (1949) 


Colorized version: https://youtu.be/q9l8vrex-JM 

Director: B. Reeves Eason 
Writers: Ron Ormond, Arthur St. Claire, Frank Wisbar 
Stars: James Millican, Mary Beth Hughes, Reed Hadley 
Genre: Noir Western,
